From: "Jack E. Turner" <jeturner@idworld.net>

[Re: spread of disease to developed countries]
The intentional introduction (regardless of motive) would constitute nothing
less than bioterrorism.
There must be better ways to raise the consciousness of the developed world
to these problem. One way is to speak to non-heath people and explain the
depth of the issues in non clinical terms. Another is to publish non-jargon
articles in the popular (credible) press explaining the various problems
clearly.
Jack
